description:
Below Deck - Season 3, Episode 14




Reunion, Part 1

Kate and Amy let Rocky know what they really think of her work ethic (or lack thereof). Eddie opens up about how his personal drama affected his ability to lead the crew, and Emile reveals how he took matters into his own hands after Rocky's rejection. Deckhand Don returns to face the cast for the first time since his sudden resignation, and Captain Lee explains why Chef Leon and his beef cheeks had to go. Tensions rise as Kate is accused of drinking on duty the night of the galley fire.




Original Air Date: 24-Nov-2015
